OL,3,CReeves backs Burnham for PM despite
OL,4,Cspeculation of who will be next
OL,5,Cchancellor
OL,7,FRachel Reeves says she is "backing"
OL,8,FAndy Burnham to be the UK's next prime
OL,9,Fminister amid speculation she could be
OL,10,Freplaced as chancellor if he takes
OL,11,Foffice.
OL,13,FSpeaking to broadcasters on Thursday,
OL,14,FReeves would not confirm whether she
OL,15,Fwould accept another role.
OL,17,FShe said she was "not going to pre-
OL,18,Fempt the decision that the new prime
OL,19,Fminister will make" and confirmed that
OL,20,Fshe supports Burnham's campaign to
OL,21,Fbecome leader.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
