FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782400703
OL,3,CReeves backs Burnham for PM despite
OL,4,Cspeculation of who will be next
OL,5,Cchancellor
OL,7,FThe former Manchester Mayor, who has
OL,8,Femerged as the frontrunner to replace
OL,9,FSir Keir Starmer, is yet to comment on
OL,10,Fwhat his choice of chancellor would be.
OL,12,FOne potential successor is Energy
OL,13,FSecretary Ed Miliband, but some Labour
OL,14,Ffigures have warned that he would not
OL,15,Fbe right for the country's economy.
OL,17,FReeves argued that whoever does take
OL,18,Fon her role next will find the economy
OL,19,Fin a better place than she did,
OL,20,Fwithout a "black hole in the public
OL,21,Ffinances".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
