PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782400703
OL,3,CReeves backs Burnham for PM despite
OL,4,Cspeculation of who will be next
OL,5,Cchancellor
OL,7,FShe said: "I hope that whoever is
OL,8,FChancellor in the future, whenever
OL,9,Fthat future may be, sticks to what I'm
OL,10,Fdoing because it is beginning to bear
OL,11,Ffruit, and we are seeing that
OL,12,Finvestment return to the economy, that
OL,13,Fgrowth return to the economy, and
OL,14,Fcrucially, that stability, so that
OL,15,Fbusinesses can plan and invest in the
OL,16,Ffuture."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
