OL,3,CReeves backs Burnham for PM despite
OL,4,Cspeculation of who will be next
OL,5,Cchancellor
OL,7,FWhen Starmer resigned on Downing
OL,8,FStreet on Monday, Reeves was not
OL,9,Fstanding in the group of staffers and
OL,10,Fministers supporting him, but was
OL,11,Flater seen at the welcome event for
OL,12,FBurnham as a new MP.
OL,14,FReeves said that "no one could doubt"
OL,15,Fher commitment to Starmer in recent
OL,16,Fyears and pointed to her record of
OL,17,Fbeing "by his side for six years".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
