OL,3,CReeves backs Burnham for PM despite
OL,4,Cspeculation of who will be next
OL,5,Cchancellor
OL,7,FBurnham is still currently the only
OL,8,Fpotential candidate for the role of
OL,9,Fleader after Starmer's Chief
OL,10,FSecretary, Darren Jones, ruled himself
OL,11,Fout of the race on Wednesday.
OL,13,FFormer Health Secretary Wes Streeting,
OL,14,Fwho had previously indicated he would
OL,15,Frun, also rowed in behind Burnham on
OL,16,FMonday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
