OL,3,CReeves backs Burnham for PM despite
OL,4,Cspeculation of who will be next
OL,5,Cchancellor
OL,7,FFormer armed forces minister Al Carns,
OL,8,Fwho resigned earlier this month in a
OL,9,Frow over defence spending, remains a
OL,10,Fpossible contender, calling for a
OL,11,F"proper debate" on the country's
OL,12,Ffuture.
OL,14,FCarns has not formally announced a
OL,15,Fleadership bid, but he has also
OL,16,Frepeatedly refused to rule himself out
OL,17,Fas a potential candidate.
