OL,3,CReeves backs Burnham for PM despite
OL,4,Cspeculation of who will be next
OL,5,Cchancellor
OL,7,FBurnham's potential takeover has drawn
OL,8,Fattention from US President, Donald
OL,9,FTrump who said the new Makerfield MP
OL,10,Fis "extremely liberal" and "probably
OL,11,Fwon't open up the North Sea" for oil
OL,12,Fdrilling.
OL,14,FHe has been critical of Trump in the
OL,15,Fpast, describing US politics as
OL,16,F"polarised" and "poisonous" while on
OL,17,Fthe campaign trail in June.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@KO]xD@QOUxD@[O]
